#include<stdio.h>
#include<iostream>
#include<math.h>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
long long n,x;
cin>>n;
double h,d,s,t1,t2,y;
while(n--)
{
  cin>>h>>d>>s;
  t1=sqrt((2*h)/32);
  t2=d/s;
  cin>>x;
  while(x--)
  {
      cin>>y;
      t2+=y;
  }
  if(t1>=t2)
     cout<<"Y"<<endl;
   else
      cout<<"N"<<endl;
}
return 0;
}
